Finance::Quote::Hollywood extends Finance::Quote to fetch quotes from
the Hollywood Stock Exchange.  It's mainly intended as a bit of fun,
so you can see HSX game prices in your favourite Finance::Quote stock
quotes program.

The prerequisites are

    * Finance::Quote
    * HTML::TableExtract (which Finance::Quote needs anyway)
    * Regexp::Common
    * LWP version 5.814 or higher
    * Perl version 5.6 or higher


The Finance::Quote::Hollywood home page is

    http://www.geocities.com/user42_kevin/finance-quote-hollywood/index.html

The Finance::Quote home page is

    http://finance-quote.sourceforge.net

The Hollywood Stock Exchange home page is

    http://www.hsx.com
